</header><main class="page-shell"><section class="section"><div class="container profile-layout"><div class="panel profile-media reveal"><img src="/assets/img/aux-portrait-bw.jpg" alt="Aux portrait black and white"></div><div class="panel profile-copy reveal"><div class="eyebrow">About Aux</div><h1>Auxilium</h1><p>Aux is an LMS administrator and instructional design professional specializing in medical-field instruction, advanced multimedia integration, and production workflows. His work includes building training systems and digital learning experiences for orthopedic education and government hospital environments.</p><p>He brings a strong background in multimedia production, combining instructional strategy with video, design, and technical systems thinking to improve how organizations deliver training at scale. Current focus areas include live broadcasting and broadcast workflows built with Unreal Engine 5.</p><div class="stat-grid"><div class="spec-item"><div class="eyebrow">Core function</div><strong class="display">LMS administration</strong><p class="small">Workflow architecture, reporting, support, process structure, and platform stewardship.</p></div><div class="spec-item"><div class="eyebrow">Secondary lane</div><strong class="display">Instructional design</strong><p class="small">Training systems, multimedia learning, content sequencing, and delivery at scale.</p></div></div><div class="spec-list"><div class="spec-item"><div class="eyebrow">Specialties</div><div class="skill-list"><span class="badge red">Moodle</span><span class="badge">MySQL</span><span class="badge">Excel</span><span class="badge">Power Query</span><span class="badge">Process automation</span><span class="badge">Video systems</span><span class="badge">Multimedia production</span><span class="badge">Training workflows</span></div></div><div class="spec-item"><div class="eyebrow">Working thesis</div><p>Build systems that are practical, scalable, and technically honest. Reduce friction. Improve outputs. Keep the workflow legible.</p></div><div class="spec-item"><div class="eyebrow">Current interests</div><p>GitHub Pages publishing, real free AI utilities, advanced creator workflows, systems automation, live broadcasting, and Unreal Engine 5 pipeline design.</p></div></div></div></div></section></main><footer class="footer">
